ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of DWIGHT BALL of Deer Lake, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Development Investment Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in place of Mary Ritchie, whose term has expired.
